        " نِفَاسِهَا لَمْ يَنْشُرْ لَهَا دِيوَانٌ يَوْمَ اَلْقِيَامَةِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.378 - The Imam (as) said:\n\"If a woman dies during childbirth (in her postpartum state), no record of her deeds will be unfurled on the Day of Resurrection.\""
        ]
      }
    },
